1
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:32,960
[Cage of Shadows]

2
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:36,130
[Episode 7]

3
00:01:37,130 --> 00:01:38,020
Master.

4
00:01:38,050 --> 00:01:40,800
This is the new drug recently sent
from the Elite Academy.

5
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:42,930
Its effect is even better than before.

6
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:44,360
Within half a year,

7
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:46,660
the elites will surely be addicted to it.

8
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:48,280
And once they stop taking it,

9
00:01:48,810 --> 00:01:49,920
they will become irritable and restless,

10
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,000
suffering a fate worse than death,

11
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,720
until they waste away and die.

12
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,480
Good.

13
00:02:12,890 --> 00:02:14,920
But this alone is not enough.

14
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,200
May I ask, Master,

15
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,070
what dissatisfaction do you have?

16
00:02:18,070 --> 00:02:19,240
I have painstakingly

17
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:21,240
managed this Lingya Tower,

18
00:02:21,900 --> 00:02:24,420
not only to weaken their minds,

19
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:26,700
but also to strengthen my own power.

20
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:29,079
Please enlighten me, Master.

21
00:02:29,079 --> 00:02:30,740
Why hasn't that batch of money

22
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,880
arrived yet?

23
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,930
Is it because you have slacked off,

24
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:38,530
or because you can't
keep your subordinates in line?

25
00:02:40,460 --> 00:02:41,920
I have failed in my duty.

26
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,670
Please punish me, Master.

27
00:02:43,670 --> 00:02:45,420
You don't have to be like this.

28
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:47,240
If your subordinates are disobedient,

29
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,300
just replace them.

30
00:02:48,490 --> 00:02:49,810
It's no big deal.

31
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,480
Get up.

32
00:02:50,500 --> 00:02:53,660
Master,
I will urge them as soon as possible.

33
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:56,040
When old-timers stay
in this tower too long,

34
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:58,630
they inevitably flaunt their seniority

35
00:02:58,650 --> 00:03:00,250
and become self-righteous.

36
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:03,160
To achieve great things,

37
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:04,960
you must be absolutely ruthless

38
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,800
when the time calls for it.

39
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:08,460
You are right, Master.

40
00:03:10,060 --> 00:03:11,990
This matter is of great importance

41
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,730
and allows no mistakes.

42
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:14,880
Yes.

43
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:31,960
I heard you mention before

44
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,520
that the man was slashed
on the neck by you,

45
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,850
nearly losing his life.

46
00:03:50,930 --> 00:03:53,120
There is actually such a big hole here.

47
00:04:04,810 --> 00:04:06,980
[Zan Hua]

48
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,160
Oh.

49
00:04:09,690 --> 00:04:11,620
Still having guests late at night?

50
00:04:23,260 --> 00:04:25,100
Three more newcomers.

51
00:04:25,340 --> 00:04:27,740
It's really getting livelier around here.

52
00:04:27,750 --> 00:04:28,350
Who is...

53
00:04:28,850 --> 00:04:29,910
Who is this person?

54
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:35,210
We are here for the death match.

55
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:37,920
I've never seen anyone

56
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,740
in such a rush to die.

57
00:04:40,330 --> 00:04:41,860
I do like you reckless fools

58
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:44,040
who don't know your place.

59
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:46,720
But it's getting late today.

60
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:48,560
If you want to take the death match,

61
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,800
wait until tomorrow.

62
00:04:49,820 --> 00:04:51,130
Tell me first,

63
00:04:51,280 --> 00:04:53,340
what is the death match on this level?

64
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,040
No rush.

65
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:01,340
We'll see if you can survive tonight.

66
00:05:05,460 --> 00:05:06,520
What are you doing?

67
00:05:06,690 --> 00:05:07,680
Don't try any of your dirty tricks,

68
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:09,030
like poisoning my food.

69
00:05:09,050 --> 00:05:10,650
I won't fall for your tricks.

70
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,200
The Gaobao kiln

71
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:14,970
has been making slow progress lately.

72
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:17,000
My Lord has urged us many times.

73
00:05:17,220 --> 00:05:18,340
About this matter,

74
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:20,980
I always feel uneasy.

75
00:05:21,080 --> 00:05:21,960
Zan Hua

76
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:23,320
is your adopted son.

77
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:24,950
With him around,

78
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:26,480
I suppose

79
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:28,440
nothing will go wrong.

80
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,560
I am

81
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:31,980
not worried about him.

82
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,080
It's just that...

83
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:34,600
If you are concerned,

84
00:05:34,930 --> 00:05:35,730
I

85
00:05:36,200 --> 00:05:38,000
am willing to offer my services.

86
00:05:58,520 --> 00:05:59,320
Holy crap!

87
00:06:00,700 --> 00:06:02,830
Why are there so many people suddenly?

88
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:05,120
Why is this place so weird?

89
00:06:08,260 --> 00:06:10,100
Who are you?

90
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,600
This cell is full.

91
00:06:27,810 --> 00:06:30,010
You can make do in my place for the night.

92
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:36,560
Come.

93
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:38,770
You three will sleep here tonight.

94
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:40,300
I've made the beds for you.

95
00:06:41,880 --> 00:06:43,680
No, don't trouble yourself.

96
00:06:47,730 --> 00:06:49,730
Why is that person carrying a sword?

97
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:53,080
Did anyone say swords aren't allowed?

98
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,450
Living with someone like that,

99
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:58,260
I wouldn't be able to rest easy

100
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:00,120
at night.

101
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:02,880
Yanzhi,

102
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:05,710
do we really have to stay here today?

103
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,480
If you don't want to stay,

104
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,500
then get out.

105
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,880
Miss Tu Ya.

106
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:20,280
These three just arrived
on this level today.

107
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,320
They don't know the rules yet,

108
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:23,440
so please don't hold it against them.

109
00:07:29,380 --> 00:07:30,180
Come.

110
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:31,440
Oh, by the way,

111
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:32,659
just call me Kou Wan.

112
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:34,710
Kou Wan.

113
00:07:34,840 --> 00:07:35,320
It's fine.

114
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:36,580
We'll do it ourselves.

115
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,250
Based on your description,

116
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,170
the poison your mother took

117
00:08:06,170 --> 00:08:09,200
was likely the work of Taiyin,
the voice-keeper before me.

118
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,480
This voice-keeper Taiyin,

119
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,800
where is he now?

120
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:12,840
The voice-keeper Taiyin,

121
00:08:12,840 --> 00:08:16,040
had always been here refining drugs
for the Tower Master before me.

122
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:18,400
Only the Tower Master
has seen his true face.

123
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:20,000
Later, because of a great contribution,

124
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,520
he was promoted to the upper level.

125
00:08:21,520 --> 00:08:22,440
So,

126
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:25,970
he is now the voice-keeper
on the third level.

127
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:30,720
If Zan Hua is the voice-keeper Taiyin,

128
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:33,900
I'd better figure out
the situation here first.

129
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:38,990
Could it be

130
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:41,250
that there's a foundry inside?

131
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:51,920
Who is it?

132
00:09:52,430 --> 00:09:53,390
Come out!

133
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:03,760
If you don't come out,

134
00:10:04,760 --> 00:10:06,690
don't blame me for being ruthless.

135
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,280
Zhuang Wujiu.

136
00:10:33,530 --> 00:10:35,720
You are not staying down below
where you belong,

137
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:37,850
but sneaking around here.

138
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:40,250
What bad idea are you cooking up again?

139
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:42,760
The Tower Master is dissatisfied
with the coin delivery progress,

140
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:44,880
so I was ordered
to come to the Gaobao kiln

141
00:10:44,880 --> 00:10:46,080
to inspect the situation.

142
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:48,160
You may rest assured
and report back to the Tower Master

143
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:49,890
that we will finish the task on schedule.

144
00:10:49,890 --> 00:10:50,730
That's good.

145
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:55,920
Zhuang Wujiu.

146
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:59,240
Finish your inspection
and leave immediately.

147
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,760
You are not welcome here.

148
00:11:01,170 --> 00:11:02,570
You and I bear no grudges.

149
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,440
Why act like this?

150
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:06,230
I know what you're here for.

151
00:11:07,280 --> 00:11:08,240
Rest assured.

152
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:09,860
As long as I am here,

153
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:12,740
don't even think about
getting close to her.

154
00:11:33,730 --> 00:11:35,380
Why are there so many people?

155
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:37,220
Is someone going to die again?

156
00:11:39,460 --> 00:11:41,590
What are we competing in on this level?

157
00:11:45,550 --> 00:11:46,630
Everyone!

158
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,880
This round of the death match

159
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:01,320
is called the Golden Cave.

160
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,280
Golden Cave?

161
00:12:04,530 --> 00:12:05,660
What do you think we have to do?

162
00:12:05,660 --> 00:12:06,400
Who knows?

163
00:12:06,420 --> 00:12:07,420
It's very simple.

164
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,760
You will be randomly paired up

165
00:12:09,880 --> 00:12:10,980
into groups of two.

166
00:12:11,060 --> 00:12:13,190
Roll the dice to determine the winner.

167
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:14,960
The game lasts for three rounds.

168
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:16,600
Those who win three consecutive rounds

169
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:18,710
can not only leave the third level,

170
00:12:18,810 --> 00:12:20,600
but also take away as much gold

171
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:23,090
as you want from here.

172
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:24,420
Why is there so much gold?

173
00:12:24,420 --> 00:12:26,480
Something's wrong. It must be a trap.

174
00:12:27,280 --> 00:12:28,340
Better be careful.

175
00:12:28,880 --> 00:12:29,810
I am not playing.

176
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:33,260
I've hated gambling my whole life.

177
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:35,470
This is the death match.

178
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:36,650
If you don't play...

179
00:12:36,650 --> 00:12:37,830
What if I don't play?

180
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:40,680
Come.

181
00:12:40,850 --> 00:12:42,040
Show her.

182
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:09,400
Everyone.

183
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:12,960
Now, you will be randomly
divided into pairs.

184
00:13:13,880 --> 00:13:16,360
There are dice
and a dice cup on each table.

185
00:13:16,540 --> 00:13:18,960
The mute servant will judge the outcome.

186
00:13:19,140 --> 00:13:21,320
The winners will advance
to the next round.

187
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:22,720
As for the losers...

188
00:13:24,520 --> 00:13:26,320
Well, you just saw what happens.

189
00:13:26,900 --> 00:13:28,700
They get thrown down, of course,

190
00:13:28,910 --> 00:13:30,770
and get their 'Third Eye' opened.

191
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:34,840
Let's not stand at the same table.

192
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:37,640
That way,
we won't have to play against each other.

193
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:39,060
Dao.

194
00:13:39,090 --> 00:13:40,150
Don't say any more.

195
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:42,340
I don't want to gamble,

196
00:13:42,950 --> 00:13:44,600
but I have to stay alive first.

197
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:45,560
Everyone, hurry up!

198
00:13:45,560 --> 00:13:46,840
Don't dilly-dally.

199
00:13:47,280 --> 00:13:49,640
Gamble early or late,
you'll still have to gamble.

200
00:13:49,640 --> 00:13:51,640
Die early or late, you'll still die.

201
00:13:51,640 --> 00:13:53,240
If you don't get to the table,

202
00:13:54,180 --> 00:13:56,380
I'll throw you all in to feed the snakes.

203
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:06,640
Is this game really purely based on luck,

204
00:14:06,640 --> 00:14:08,220
just comparing the numbers?

205
00:14:08,220 --> 00:14:09,220
I don't think so.

206
00:14:09,500 --> 00:14:11,060
The simpler the game,

207
00:14:11,090 --> 00:14:13,090
the less you can let your guard down.

208
00:14:34,690 --> 00:14:36,570
Why is Qi here too?

209
00:14:36,770 --> 00:14:39,520
Could Master have brought him here again?

210
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:43,520
Is everyone ready?

211
00:14:43,880 --> 00:14:45,470
Golden Cave.

212
00:14:45,640 --> 00:14:46,560
Round 1.

213
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:49,290
Begin!

214
00:14:50,950 --> 00:14:53,210
[First Meeting]

215
00:15:08,580 --> 00:15:09,940
It's been hard

216
00:15:10,680 --> 00:15:12,040
on you lately.

217
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:13,800
Not at all.

218
00:15:15,920 --> 00:15:17,320
If it weren't for Master,

219
00:15:17,880 --> 00:15:20,840
I wouldn't know how to keep going.

220
00:15:28,230 --> 00:15:29,680
I made this for you, Master.

221
00:15:29,680 --> 00:15:32,360
I call it the filigree bangle.

222
00:15:33,520 --> 00:15:35,640
Someday, when you wear it

223
00:15:35,680 --> 00:15:37,640
and we storm Lingya Tower together,

224
00:15:37,640 --> 00:15:38,720
we will surely be invincible

225
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:39,440
and completely unstoppable.

